Daewoo Shipbuilding Hasn’t Yet Decided on Building South African Shipyard

-- B y   S e o n j i n   C h a
-- 
2011-07-04T06:08:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-04/daewoo-shipbuilding-hasn-t-yet-decided-on-building-south-african-shipyard.html
Daewoo Shipbuilding & Marine
Engineering Co. hasn’t made any decision about a possible plan
to build a shipyard in   South Africa , it said in an e-mail to
Bloomberg News today. Business Day earlier reported Daewoo wants
to build a shipyard in the African nation, which may cost 40
billion rand ($6 billion).                To contact the reporter on this story:
